# Canonicalize the old Pages host → the outlay-ai.com brand domain.
# Host-scoped source: matches only requests served on modelpilot.pages.dev, so it
# never loops outlay-ai.com onto itself. (If Cloudflare treats the source as a
# path it simply no-ops; the per-page <link rel=canonical> carries the SEO signal
# either way.)
https://modelpilot.pages.dev/* https://outlay-ai.com/:splat 301

